org.steveleach.scoresheet.model

Class ScoresheetModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.steveleach.scoresheet.model.ScoresheetModel

  • public class ScoresheetModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Information about an ice hockey game, including the events that took place during the game.

    The primary component of a ScoresheetModel is a list of GameEvent objects.

    Author:
    Steve Leach
